        </svg>
        Join Our Discord
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        GitHub for code and issues. Discord for questions and chat. Every bit of help - code or donation - keeps this project alive.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
